MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-2879. State v. Parks.

Clark App. No. 96CA89. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Clark County. It appearing to the court that appellant did not serve the other party in this case in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. XIV(2)(A),

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this case be, and hereby is, dismissed.
